snippet.title: Episode 2: What really happened between Amber and Johnny?
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Spiritual Sinners podcast! Today's episode is all about the situation between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp.

Depp was wrongfully accused of domestic violence towards Amber back in 2015.

His career and reputation were negatively impacted by these slanderous accusations, and he ended up suing her for $50,000,000.

Recently, there has been audio of a conversation between Heard and Depp which tells an entirely different story. Turns out that Amber was the abuser all along.

#JusticeforJohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp
